    "ideation": "The stopwatch emoji is about the tension of time, the mechanical rhythm of a clock, and the sudden freeze of a split-second measurement. I'm personifying the stopwatch as a high-precision instrument: the eyes represent the ticking gears and the mouth represents the passage of time itself. The sequence begins with a rapid, mechanical 'ticking' motion where the eyes twitch side-to-side in a rhythmic pulse. As the timer approaches zero, the tension builds—the eyes narrow and the mouth becomes a dense, fast-moving wave. The climax is the 'STOP'—an instant, frozen capture where everything goes wide and white-hot, before settling into a cool, blue 'memory' of the recorded time. The colors move from a ticking amber to a frantic neon green, then a stark white flash, ending in a static technical blue.",
